Prerequisites 
=============
* Apache maven 3.0.3 or higher
* Java 1.6

How to setup development environment
====================================
* Clone this repository
* Download Eclipse for RCP and RAP Developers from http://www.eclipse.org/downloads
* Open Eclipse and choose a workspace location
* Install M2Eclipse plugin from Eclipse Marketplace. Go to Help > Eclipse Marketplace, and find "Maven Integration for Eclipse"; click on install
* [Optional] configure local maven instalation. Go to Window > Preferences > Maven > Installations and add your local Maven Runtime
* Import project into Eclipse. Go to File > Import > Maven > Existing Maven Projects, and select the root of your cloned repository. Click on finish.
* Add the PDE plugin libraries doing right click in your project -> Configure -> Convert to Plug-in Projects...
* From command line go to the root of the cloned project and run 'mvn clean package' to copy the needed libraries into the libraries

